  "wpt": true,
  "wpt_descr": "New tests:\n- Character-level mirroring: checks that when switching text direction the codepoints of the characters change to the corresponding BidiMirrored equivalent (e.g. right to left parentheses)\n- Glyph-level mirroring: checks that the rtlm font feature is supported and that a specific glyph is used for certain characters when switching text direction.",
